<li>A transferable $150 purchase credit from <a href="https://elkcreekcompany.net/">Elk Creek Company</a>, toward the purchase of any pre-1899 antique gun. There is <b>no paperwork required </b>for delivery of pre-1899 guns into most states, making them the last bastion of firearms purchasing privacy!</li>
</ol>
<p>Round 89 ends on July 31st, so get busy writing and <a href="https://survivalblog.com/contact/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">e-mail</a> us your entry. Remember that there is a <strong>1,500-word minimum</strong>, and that articles on practical “how to” skills for survival have an advantage in the judging.</p>
									</div><!-- .entry-content -->
