			<a class="post-featured-image" href="https://survivalblog.com/editors-quote-day-1132/" title="The Editors&#039; Quote of the Day:"  style="background-image: url(https://survivalblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/torahscroll.jpg)" > </a>
